# Face-gallery images are PII (household members). Keep the folder
# structure, .gitkeep files, and README.md tracked so the layout ships,
# but the images themselves must never be committed. Canonical store
# is the filesystem on the Pi (and rsync'd to the Mac for the
# enhancement server — see docs/enhancement_tier.md).
tool/face_gallery/**/*.jpg
tool/face_gallery/**/*.jpeg
tool/face_gallery/**/*.png
tool/face_gallery/**/*.JPG
tool/face_gallery/**/*.JPEG
tool/face_gallery/**/*.PNG
.venv-monitoring-yolo/
/scripts/deploy_pi_msvallee.sh

# Auto-generated session state (written by post-commit hook)
SESSION_STATE.md
